<p>Welcome to the eighth episode of 15 Minutes In Hell.</p><p>Today&#8217;s guest is political commentator and news anchor <a href="https://twitter.com/chrislhayes">Chris Hayes</a> of <a href="https://www.msnbc.com/all">MSNBC</a>. </p><p>We talked about the growth of cult-like grifters in the media, how American democracy is in a trust crisis, and how doing television scratches the itch when you&#8217;re a theater kid. Chris is <a href="https://www.msnbc.com/msnbc-podcast/why-is-this-happening-chris-hayes">currently on tour with his podcast Why Is This Happening</a>. </p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ylitz-NmRno">The 15 Minutes In Hell Theme</a> is written and performed by<a href="https://www.patreon.com/Eve6ix"> Eve6</a>.</p><p>If you&#8217;ve enjoyed<a href="http://wheresyoured.at/podcast"> this podcast</a>, subscribe free to Ed&#8217;s newsletter<a href="http://wheresyoured.at/"> Where&#8217;s Your Ed At</a>, or join us at the<a href="http://chat.wheresyoured.at/"> Where&#8217;s Your Ed At Discord</a>.</p><p></p>